				<h3>Re: BitTorrent Sync on stora???</h3>
				<div class="date"><img src="./styles/absolution/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" />Posted: <strong>Mon Sep 21, 2015 3:14 am</strong></div>
				<div class="author">by <strong>pippone</strong></div>
				<div class="content">you may have to run the btsync daemon specifying a command line option to set the listen port:<br /><br />./btsync --webui.listen &lt;yourstoraip&gt;:8888<br /><br />it worked for me</div>
